        "c1dd452d-6764-44cf-84c5-766f79a83591": {
          "type": "Image",
          "settings": {
            "image1": "shopify://shop_images/cnc-laser-cutting-of-metal-modern-industrial-tech-2021-08-26-23-00-42-utc.jpg",
            "video_alignment": "right",
            "title": "The Art of Metal Fabrication in Retail: Experience the Vanguard Difference",
            "video_description": "<p>Vanguard Store Fixtures welcomes you to a world where metal takes on new meaning through our expert metal fabrication services. Our capabilities extend beyond mere production; we blend technical expertise, creative design, and an understanding of retail functionality to produce metal fixtures that are robust, stylish, and fit for purpose. Every piece we create is a testament to our commitment to craftsmanship and our ability to transform metal into an integral part of your retail journey.</p>"
          }
        },
        "f25fc9c2-b553-4833-aac6-b43c2850a464": {
          "type": "Image",
          "settings": {
            "image1": "shopify://shop_images/bangkok-metal-store-2021-08-26-17-13-53-utc.jpg",
            "video_alignment": "left",
            "title": "",
            "video_description": "<p>With years of industry experience, we have honed our skills to meet the unique challenges of the retail sector. Be it custom shelving units, intricate display stands, or sleek checkout counters, our metal fabrication solutions are crafted to enhance your store's aesthetics while ensuring seamless operations. We not only build these elements but also design them to interact effectively with your retail space, which include but are not limited t:</p><ul><li><strong>Grocery Stores:</strong> Metal fixtures in grocery stores include shelving units, produce bins, and specialized display cases for different food items.</li><li><strong>Clothing Stores:</strong> Metal racks, shelves, and display stands are essential for showcasing apparel and accessories.</li><li><strong>Electronics Stores:</strong> Custom metal display units are often used to hold and highlight electronic devices, providing a sleek and modern look..</li><li><strong>Sporting Goods Stores:</strong> Metal fixtures are used for displaying a variety of sports equipment, from bikes to outdoor gear.</li><li><strong>Bookstores:</strong> Metal bookshelves, display stands, and sign holders are commonly used.</li><li><strong>Home Improvement Stores:</strong> Heavy-duty metal shelving units and racks are needed to display a wide range of hardware and home improvement supplies.</li><li><strong>Jewelry Stores:</strong> Metal display cases, often combined with glass, are used to securely showcase jewelry pieces.</li><li><strong>Convenience Stores:</strong> Metal fixtures in convenience stores include shelving units, beverage and food display stands, and checkout counters.</li><li><strong>Pharmacies:</strong> Metal fixtures are used for medicine cabinets, shelving, and checkout counters.</li><li><strong>Cosmetics Stores:</strong> Custom metal fixtures for product display units, testers, and cash wrap counters.</li><li><strong>Pet Stores:</strong> Metal fixtures for cage units, product display shelves, and checkout stations.</li><li><strong>Toy Stores:</strong> Metal display units and shelves to organize and display toys.</li></ul>"
          }
        },
        "d7cceaf7-b520-492c-8eff-8da75c49693d": {
          "type": "Image",
          "settings": {
            "image1": "shopify://shop_images/2_close-up-metal-pipes-arranged-parallel-2021-08-30-06-51-21-utc_50.jpg",
            "video_alignment": "right",
            "title": "",
            "video_description": "<p>Choose Vanguard Store Fixtures for metal fabrication services that transform the ordinary into extraordinary. Our expertise in retail dynamics, commitment to quality, and knowledge of consumer behavior make us an unmatched partner for your store fixture needs. Engage with us today and experience the revolution in retail spaces that our metal fabrication services bring. With Vanguard Store Fixtures, your store becomes a symphony of form, function, and superior design.</p>"
          }
        },
        "064f393a-781b-4465-96df-a1bff3e5f44d": {
          "type": "Image",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "image1": "shopify://shop_images/an-angle-grinder-with-a-cutting-disc-saws-a-metal-2023-04-03-22-42-44-utc_50.jpg",
